snippet.title: Elon Musk Denies Having Threesome With Amber Heard and Cara Delevingne
snippet.description:
Elon Musk Denies Having Threesome With Amber Heard and Cara Delevingne..
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UChjDtGelMNkllI5S22oO_aA?sub_confirmation=1
 The Tesla founder breaks his silence on the rumors suggesting he was involved in a 'three-way affair' with Johnny Depp's ex-wife and the 'Suicide Squad' enchantress.   Jun 19, 2020   AceShowbiz - Elon Musk has denied reports he enjoyed a "threesome affair" with Amber Heard and Cara Delevingne.    The new dad has been linked to a sex tryst involving the actresses as part of a defamation case filed against Heard by her ex-husband Johnny Depp, and Daily Mail sources claim the "Pirates of the Caribbean" star's lawyers want to quiz Cara about the rumoured "three-way affair," which reportedly began at Depp's downtown Los Angeles penthouse in 2016 after Heard split from the movie star.         Johnny's legal team has reportedly obtained an image of a woman "closely resembling Delevingne riding the private elevator to Depp's penthouse."    But in a new statement, Musk insists he and model and actress Cara are "friends," insisting, "We've never been intimate."    "She would confirm this.
